public class GoldenFogDoor extends edu.monash.fit2099.engine.positions.Ground implements Travelable
GoldenFogDoor which inherits from Ground and implements Travelable as it can be used "travel" to other GameMaps. Created by:

      GoldenFogDoor Constructor. Calls parent class to set inherited data attributes. Adds the CAN_TRAVEL capability to signify this Golden Fog Door allows the Player to travel to another map.
